item.title: 【Albums (lossy)】MP3 - Taylor Swift - Eras World Tour (Live in Los Angeles) MP3 12-13-23 [51 Tracks Digitally Mastered]
item.description:
EACH TRACK HAS ITS METADATA WITH THE ARTWORK. Includes the following. Each track was mixed and mastered by me, edited to flow into each other and the bonus tracks have also been added to their proper place within the setlist, merged seamlessly so it feels like they never left. All speeches were split into their own tracks and the standing ovations and long gaps have been removed to improve flow.
